### Tạo hóa đơn mới
POST http://localhost:3001/api/bills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "695f5666fd4ec837338d2284",
  "totalAmount": 150000,
  "status": "UNPAID"
}

### Lấy danh sách hóa đơn
GET http://localhost:3001/api/bills?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Lấy chi tiết hóa đơn theo ID
GET http://localhost:3001/api/bills/6963b28ccde9efec3ce8899f
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Lấy thống kê doanh thu
GET http://localhost:3001/api/bills/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
